00:23:35.910 --> 00:23:37.510
no puedo comunicarme con ella.

00:23:39.350 --> 00:23:40.550
Bien, gracias.

00:23:46.420 --> 00:23:49.540
[Contacto]

00:23:49.540 --> 00:23:52.220
[Ruanruan]

